reviewText: I have read the books and seen the videos from Prof. Leonard Holifield and have been waiting for this video for years! I now understand why he is one of the countrys leading experts on hand-to-hand combat and most respected martial art instructors in the world. The video covers his childhood, martial arts career, military career and protecting former Alabama Chief Justice Roy Moore "The Ten Commandments Judge". A true America Hero. A must see!
